Clean Street is a full-stack civic engagement platform that enables citizens to report, track, and manage local public issues such as garbage dumps, potholes, water leakage, and broken streetlights.
The system improves transparency and efficiency by allowing users, authorities, and communities to interact through real-time updates, voting, and feedback.

✨ Features:
Report issues with location, image, and description.
Track complaint status (Received, In Review, Resolved).
Voting & 💬 commenting system for community engagement.
Admin dashboard to manage complaints and users.
Authentication (OTP/Login).

🏗️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB
